tweet: I made it a point to thank @POTUS, @VP, and @EsperDOD for their leadership with the next battleground – space. The Space Force is needed, and I am committed to supporting the program as Ranking Member of the Appropriations Committee. pic.twitter.com/Ouq1idYYr8

It was an honor to join @POTUS, @VP, and other patriots at the welcoming ceremony for @EsperDOD as the 27th Secretary of Defense. I am confident that with Secretary Esper at the helm, the future of our armed services looks better and brighter than ever. pic.twitter.com/F5CKPAdBxN

I have known Secretary Esper for many years - he is an outstanding leader and a true patriot, and he has the right mix of experience and character to get the job done. I am pleased he has been confirmed to serve as 27th Secretary of Defense. https://twitter.com/cspan/status/1153706711322157057 …
